es.csic.iiia.bms.factors
Class CompositeIndependentFactor<T>

java.lang.Object
  es.csic.iiia.bms.factors.AbstractFactor<T>
      es.csic.iiia.bms.factors.CompositeIndependentFactor<T>
Type Parameters:
T - Type of the factor's identity.
All Implemented Interfaces:
CommunicationAdapter<T>, Factor<T>
Deprecated. 

public class CompositeIndependentFactor<T>
extends AbstractFactor<T>
implements CommunicationAdapter<T>

This factor composes (sums) an independent cost/utility factor with some other inner (non-independent) factor.

The resulting complexity is the same as that of the inner factor.

Author:
Marc Pujol
